Enter sales for day 1: 1500
Enter sales for day 2: 2000
Enter sales for day 3: 1800
Enter sales for day 4: 2200
Enter sales for day 5: 1700
Enter sales for day 6: 2500
Enter sales for day 7: 3000

Total weekly sales = 14700.00
